(22, '10 ex-governing body members of co-op bank arrested for fraud', '																		Police also registered another case today against the same persons for taking loans from the cooperative bank by forging fake documents in the name of a woman without her knowledge.', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com/content/dam/mm/en/news/nation/images/2016/Oct/13/arrest.jpg.image.275.145.jpg'),
