(24, 'SC witnesses high drama as justice Katju makes historic appearance', '																		Justice Katju and Rohatgi who represented the Kerala government were taken off guard by the sudden initiation of the contempt proceedings against the former.', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com/content/dam/mm/en/news/kerala/images/2016/Nov/11/supreme-court-katju.jpg.image.275.145.jpg'),
(25, 'Soumya murder: SC rejects review petition, contempt notice slapped on justice Katju', '																		The Supreme Court on Friday rejected the review petition filed by Kerala government and Soumya"s mother seeking death penalty for Govindachamy for raping 23-year-old Soumya.', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com/content/dam/mm/en/news/nation/images/2016/Nov/11/katju-india.jpg.image.275.145.jpg'),
(26, 'Crime branch to probe JNU missing student"s case', '																		Delhi police has transferred the case of the missing Jawaharlal Nehru University student Najeeb Ahmed to its crime branch, an official said.', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com/content/dam/mm/en/news/just-in/images/2016/Feb/20/jnu-campus.jpg.image.275.145.jpg'),
(27, 'Heavy artillery charges herald complete breakdown in Indo-Pak relations', '																		The tacit understanding between the militaries of India and Pakistan has gone for a toss, going by the allegation by the Pakistan establishment about heavy artillery offensive along the Line of Control.', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com/content/dam/mm/en/news/world/images/2016/Nov/12/bofors-gun.jpg.image.275.145.jpg'),
(28, 'Using bedsheets as rope, two prisoners escape from Warangal jail', '																		According to officials, the two prisoners escaped by using bedsheets as a rope.', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com/content/dam/mm/en/news/kerala/images/march-15/al-umma-double-life-term-jail.jpg.image.275.145.jpg'),
