(30, '"Shameless": Katju hits back at SC bench for plotting "surgical strike" against him', '																		A day after he was slapped with a contempt of court notice by SC over the Soumya murder case, Markandey Katju said what happened in court was a "pre-planned surgical strike".', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com/content/dam/mm/en/news/nation/images/2016/Nov/12/markandey-katju-sc-soumya-murder.jpg.image.275.145.jpg'),
(31, 'PM Modi, Abe ride on Japan"s iconic Shinkansen bullet train: pix', ' 																		Modi and Abe travelled in the train, whose speed ranges from 240 km per hour to 320 km per hour, from Tokyo to Kobe, a city on Osaka Bay in Japan.', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com', 'http://www.manoramaonline.com/content/dam/mm/en/news/world/images/2016/Nov/12/modi-abe-shinkansen.jpg.image.275.145.jpg'),
