(4, 'Banks, ATMs mobbed for third day, cash chaos continues (Lead, correcting error in last para)', ' Tempers flared at many places outside banks and ATMs on Saturday as tens of thousands of anxious people waited for the third consecutive day to deposit or exchange their spiked currency or take out cash.. With millions of people queuing up outside banks and ATMs  the RBI has asked people to be patient as the banks have enough currency for exchange..', ''),
