(6, 'Hasty, unplanned demonetization by government: Congress', ' The Congress party on Saturday slammed the Narendra Modi government for acting "In haste and in an unplanned" manner by demonetizing Rs 500 and Rs 1 000 notes  and said the nation was suffering due to it.. The former Union Minister further said that 86 per cent of the total value of currency notes in circulation was in the denomination of Rs 500 or Rs 1 000...', ''),
