(8, 'Demonetisation a "big black scandal": Mamata', ' Ratcheting up her demand for withdrawal of the Narendra Modi-led central government"s decision to demonetise Rs 500 and Rs 1 000 currency notes  West Bengal Chief Minister Mamata Banerjee on Saturday said the move has turned out to be a"big black scandal".. Renewing her attack on Modi government for ban of old Rs. 1 000 and Rs. 500 notes  West Bengal Chief Minister Mamata Banerjee today demanded withdrawal of this "black" political decision saying it is against the common people..', ''),
(9, '2 prisoners escape from Telangana"s Warangal jail', ' Two prisoners escaped from Warangal Central Jail in Telangana early on Saturday  police said.. Two convicts serving life sentence in Central Prison Warangal in Telangana  escaped using bed sheets as ropes..', ''),
(10, '"Scotch Whisky Weeks" pairs fine malts with delectable fare (Foodie Trail-Gurugram)', ' In yet another sign that this bustling IT hub on the outskirts of the national capital has "arrived", a leading luxury hotel chain has chosen its property here to host the inaugural Scottish Whisky Weeks gala that will bring together the finest malts paired with delectable cuisine to cater to the taste buds of the most fastidious.', ''),
